data.name: GetShowroomReview
data.value: Select ShowroomReviewId, UserId, ShowroomId, ShowroomReview from [UnicoVehicle].[review].[ShowroomReview] where DeletedDate is null

data.name: GetShowroomReviewbyId
data.value: Select UserId, ShowroomId, ShowroomReview from [UnicoVehicle].[review].[ShowroomReview] where DeletedDate is null and ShowroomReviewId = @showroomReviewId

data.name: InsertShowroomReview
data.value: Insert into [UnicoVehicle].[review].[ShowroomReview] (UserId, ShowroomId, ShowroomReview, CreatedDate) values (@userId, @showroomId, @showroomReview, @createdDate)

data.name: UpdateShowroomReview
data.value: Update [UnicoVehicle].[review].[ShowroomReview] set ShowroomReview = @showroomReview, ModifiedDate = @modifiedDate where ShowroomReviewId = @showroomReviewId
